{"tid":2316273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出示律師樓文件　反駁警方指控　許智峯逐點回應傳媒　並質問警方","createTime":"2020-12-07T18:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T06:48:57.000Z","uid":261647,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"89d4a3650f80d80b6fe081297a285cfd2fd2a216","tid":2316273,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:34:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/supporthktv/posts/3436277869822743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsupporthktv%2Fposts%2F3436277869822743&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7JggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=0ba8638a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/supporthktv/posts/3436277869822743</a><br />\n<br />\n#有晒律師樓文件<br />\n#咁都叫洗黑錢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/huichifung913/posts/1685008491681340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhuichifung913%2Fposts%2F1685008491681340&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7JggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=48a55e1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/huichifung913/posts/1685008491681340</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：許智峯 Ted Hui Chi Fung<br />\n<br />\n宣布流亡才數天，港共政權繼續每天不違餘力對我及家人抹黑攻擊，包括對我及家人的銀行戶口不斷凍結滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n就警方今天對我的指控，我回應傳媒查詢如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 就去年底我發起的私人檢控抗警暴眾籌，所籌得金額由始至今只存於律師樓戶口，期間並無轉往任何其他戶口，更遑論所謂「挪用」。我在此再公開（過去已曾公開）眾籌的核數報告，光明正大，歡迎公眾查閱。<br />\n<br />\n2. 眾籌所得款項由始至今與我個人戶口及我家人戶口完全無關。若如警方所指控「金錢流向可疑」等，應該進一步公開說明細節，說明有客觀合理可疑之處，否則只流於政權對異見者的政治打壓、抹黑滋擾行為。<br />\n<br />\n3. 眾籌至今已一年，眾籌所支付的私人檢控及司法覆核案等件已經全面展開，警方突然在我宣布流亡後翌日凍結我及我全家人戶口，時間之吻合，足證行動是警方的政治報復。而眾籌的官司針對警員干犯刑事罪行，警方打壓這次眾籌本身亦有利益衝突之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n4. 警方至今未有解釋為何我及家人戶口「凍結又解凍」的情況，認為警方處事兒戲，為了政治打壓一位流亡議員而放棄整個銀行體系的信譽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmcH7yJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmcH7yJ.jpg&h=fed0eb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSdcLky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSdcLky.jpg&h=53488682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GibRgsk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGibRgsk.jpg&h=6b83f3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD2MPNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD2MPNr.jpg&h=840b9ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKLZqkU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKLZqkU.jpg&h=383f8821&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e584c86afd75fa1d32cf7fd23fc5421116039094","tid":2316273,"uid":76804,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"許智勇真係痴撚線<br />\n邊有人流亡流到佢咁高戰鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67970f765a30962568f639b942267661afb8a849","tid":2316273,"uid":44358,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e584c86afd75fa1d32cf7fd23fc5421116039094","tid":2316273,"uid":76804,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"許智勇真係痴撚線<br />\n邊有人流亡流到佢咁高戰鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:41:47.000Z","msg":"佢要流亡海外，係香港人既損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09f1d9e0b773b92037556fa13ae9e596e27b41d","tid":2316273,"uid":47384,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"狗方有咩好講<br />\n屈得就屈<br />\n單單眾籌都話黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b961dcec98a8be4f2b4059c025b2a7c6b0ed997","tid":2316273,"uid":50101,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e584c86afd75fa1d32cf7fd23fc5421116039094","tid":2316273,"uid":76804,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"許智勇真係痴撚線<br />\n邊有人流亡流到佢咁高戰鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"而家喺香港玩D咁嘅嘢下一